com.telenav.kivakit.kernel.language.collections.list.LinkedObjectList<T>
All Implemented Interfaces:
CompressibleCollection, Iterable<T>, Collection<T>, List<T>
public class LinkedObjectList<T> extends AbstractSequentialList<T> implements CompressibleCollection
A linked list of objects that adds functionality to LinkedList, including the ability to serialize with Kryo and to compress(CompressibleCollection.Method) the collection to reduce consumed space (at which point it is no longer a mutable linked list). Matching elements can be iterated with matching(Matcher).
Author:
jonathanl (shibo)
